ECB’s Draghi Not Against Giving EFSF Bank Licence, Spiegel Says

-- B y   G a b i   T h e s i n g
-- 
2011-10-03T12:26:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/ecb-s-draghi-not-against-giving-efsf-bank-licence-spiegel-says.html
Incoming European Central Bank
President  Mario Draghi  is not opposed to granting the euro
area’s temporary rescue fund a banking licence, giving it access
to the ECB’s refinancing operations,  Der Spiegel  reported
without saying where it got the information.  Draghi’s Austrian colleague  Ewald Nowotny  and ECB Vice
President Vitor Constancio are also in favor of the proposal,
the paper edition of the weekly magazine published today said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gabi Thesing at 
 gthesing@bloomberg.net  